    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device and support the regulatory submission comparison against the predicate device.",
